<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.810609>
    dc:description "FIGURES 11 – 31. Females. Holoparasitus inornatus: 11 presternal plate, sternum, paragynia; 12 sternum, paragynia, endogynium; 13 endogynium. Holoparasitus megacalcaratus: 14 ventral side of idiosoma. Holoparasitus ellipticus: 15 presternal plate and lateral platelets. Holoparasitus spp.: 16, 17 presternal plate and lateral platelets. Holoparasitus siculus: 18 epigynium; 19, 20 central prong of epigynium and endogynium; 21 endogynium. Holoparasitus algiersensis: 22 presternal plate; 23 presternal plate and sternum; 24 paragynia and epigynium; 25 endogynium. Holoparasitus eivissa: 26 presternal plate and sternum; 27 epigynium; 28, 29 endogynium under paragynia and epigynium; 30 paragynium; 31 endogynium laterally. Scale bars: 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/810609/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.810607>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 10. Females. Holoparasitus spp.: 1 ventral side of idiosoma; 2 sternum, presternal plate and lateral presternal platelets; 3 paragynium; 4 epigynium; 5 anterior part of epigynium; 6, 7 endogynium; 8 gnathosoma and gnathotectum, dorsally; 9 gnathosoma, ventrally; 10 pedipalp trochanter." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/810607/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.810611>
    dc:description "FIGURES 32 – 51. Females. Holoparasitus calpetanus: 32 presternal plate; 33 sternum; 34 paragynium; 35 endogynium covered with endogynial lamella visible between paragynia; 36 endogynium covered with endogynial lamella; 37, 38 endogynium between paragynia, two oblique aspects; 39 endogynium with endogynial lemella; 40 endogynial lamella. Holoparasitus lawrencei: 41 epigynium; 42 central prong of epigynium with subapical structure; 43, 44 endogynium, two aspects. Holoparasitus machnerti: 45 gnathotectum; 46 presternal plate, lateral platelets and sternum; 47 paragynium, posterolateral protrusion; 48 epigynium; 49 endogynium. Holoparasitus maritimus: 50 sternum; 51 endogynium. Scale bars: 32 – 34, 41 – 49 0.1 mm, 35 – 40 0.05 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/810611/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.810613>
    dc:description "FIGURES 52 – 67. Females. Holoparasitus rifensis: 52 presternal plate, lateral platelets and sternum; 53 epigynium; 54 epigynium subapical structure under central prong; 55 paragynium; 56 endogynium. Holoparasitus lunae: 57 presternal plate, lateral platelets, sternum and paragynium; 58 epigynium; 59 epigynium subapical structure; 60, 61 endogynium. Holoparasitus malleus: 62 presternal plate, lateral platelets and sternum; 63 epigynium; 64 paragynia and endogynium; 65 – 67 endogynium. Scale bars: 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/810613/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.810615>
    dc:description "FIGURES 68 – 84. Females. Holoparasitus giganteus: 68 presternal plate, lateral platelets and sternum; 69 epigynium; 70 endogynium, laterally; 71 paragynium. Holoparasitus lapalma: 72 pedipalpal trochanter posterolaterally; 73 presternal plate, lateral platelets and sternum; 74 epigynium; 75 epigynium central prong; 76 endogynium; 77 paragynium. Holoparasitus variabilis: 78 epigynium central prong; 79 endogynium; 80 endogynial stipula; 81 paragynium and endogynium. Holoparasitus anaga: 82 gnathotectum; 83 epigynium subapical structure; 84 endogynium. Scale bars: 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/810615/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.810617>
    dc:description "FIGURES 85 – 98. Females. Holoparasitus vaucheri: 85 gnathotectum; 86 paragynium; 87 epigynium; 88 endogynium. Holoparasitus franzi: 89 gnathotectum; 90 paragynium and endogynium; 91 endogynium; 92 epigynium. Holoparasitus canariensis: 93 paragynium; 94 epigynium; 95 endogynium; 96 endogynium under paragynial central prong. Holoparasitus mallorcae: 97 epigynium; 98 endogynium, lateral aspect. Scale bars: 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/810617/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.810619>
    dc:description "FIGURES 99 – 119. Females. Holoparasitus ellipticus: 99 presternal plate, lateral platelets and sternum; 100 epigynium, anterior part; 101, 102 endogynium. Holoparasitus gibber: 103 epigynium, anterior part; 104 endogynium. Holoparasitus ampullaris: 105 ventral side, genital region showing endogynium under paragynia and epigynium; 106 epigynium, anterior part; 107 – 109 endogynium, different aspects. Holoparasitus caesus: 110 gnathotectum; 111 epigynium central prong with subapical structure; 112 endogynium under subapical epigynial structure; 113 endogynium. Holoparasitus tuberculatus: 114 gnathotectum; 115 epigynial central prong with subapical structure; 116 endogynium under genital opening. Holoparasitus fortunatus: 117 gnathotectum; 118 epigynial central prong with subapical structure; 119 endogynium. Scale bar: 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/810619/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.810621>
    dc:description "FIGURES 120 – 146. Females. Holoparasitus inventus: 120 idiosoma ventral side; 121 endogynium. Holoparasitus nonaltus: 122 endogynium under paragynia and epigynial central prong; 123 epigynium, anterior part; 124 paragynia; 125, 126 endogynium. Holoparasitus peraltus: 127 epigynium, anterior part; 128 paragynia; 129 endogynium. Holoparasitus cornutus: 130 trochanter IV with lamellar process ending in two prongs; 131 ibid., distal end of segment; 132 epigynium; 133 endogynium. Holoparasitus intermedius: 134, 135 gnathotectum; 136 epigynium; 137 paragynia and endogynium. Holoparasitus hemisphaericus: 138 endogynium under paragynia and epigynium; 139, 140 epigynium; 141 endogynium; 142 endogynial lamella. Holoparasitus rhombogynialis: 143 epigynium; 144 endogynium with endogynial lamella outlined; 145 endogynial lamella; 146 endogynium, another aspect. Scale bars: 130 – 132, 139 – 146 0.1 mm, 133 0.05 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/810621/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.810623>
    dc:description "FIGURES 147 – 165. Females. Holoparasitus dallaii: 147 gv 2 pore in thicken cuticular foveola; 148 epigynium; 149, 150 endogynium. Holoparasitus globosus: 151 gv 2 pore in foveola behind coxa IV opening; 152 region of genital opening with endogynium under paragynia and epigynium; 153 epigynium; 154 endogynium; 155 endogynial lamella. Holoparasitus fovealis: 156 region of genital opening with endogynium under paragynia and epigynium; 157 epigynium; 158 – 160 endogynium. Holoparasitus amiatus: 161 gnathotectum; 162 epigynium; 163 epigynium central prong; 164, 165 endogynium. Scale bars: 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/810623/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.810627>
    dc:description "FIGURES 188 – 208. Females. Holoparasitus kerkirensis: 188 epigynium, central and lateral prongs; 189, 190 endogynium; 191 gnathotectum. Holoparasitus pollicipatus: 192 epigynium, central and lateral prongs; 193 endogynium. Holoparasitus calcaratus: 194 epigynium, central and lateral prongs; 195 endogynium. Holoparasitus paradisiacus: 196 epigynium, central and lateral prongs; 197 endogynium. Holoparasitus annulus: 198 presternal plate, lateral platelets and sternum anterior margin; 199 epigynium, anterior part; 200, 201 endogynium in situ. Holoparasitus sardensis: 202 presternal plate, lateral platelets and sternum anterior margin; 203 epigynium, anterior part; 204, 205 endogynium in situ. Holoparasitus excisus: 206 endogynium under paragynia and epigynium central prong; 207 epigynium, anterior part; 208 endogynium. Scale bars: 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/810627/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.810629>
    dc:description "FIGURES 209 – 227. Females. Holoparasitus vasilei: 209 paragynia and endogynium; 210 anterior part of epigynium and central epigynial prong with subapical structure (courtesy of Dr. I. Juvara-Bals, Nov. 2016); 211 endogynium. Holoparasitus fanes: 212, 213 epigynium central prong; 214 paragynia and epigynium central prong; 215 endogynium between paragynia; 216 endogynium. Holoparasitus crassisetosus: 217 tibia IV with thickened seta pv 1; 218 epigynium, anterior part; 219 paragynium and endogynium; 220 endogynium. Holoparasitus digitiformis: 221 epigynium, central and lateral prongs; 222, 223 paragynium and endogynium; 224 – 226 endogynium, different perspectives; 227 endogynium and endogynial lamella. Scale bars: 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/810629/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.810625>
    dc:description "FIGURES 166 – 187. Females. Holoparasitus rotulifer: 166 epigynium, central and lateral prongs; 167 – 169 endogynium. Holoparasitus pseudoperforatus: 170 epigynium; 171 paragynium; 172 epigynium subapical structure; 173, 174 endogynium, ventrally; 175 endogynium in posteroventral perspective. Holoparasitus excipuliger: 176 – 178 gnathotectum; 179 epigynium, anterior part; 180 – 182 epigynium central prong with subapical structure; 183 – 187 endogynium, different aspects. Scale bars: 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/810625/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

